1. In a bowl, mix together the soft cheese, lemon zest and juice, capers, herbs and salmon. Season to taste, then chill in the fridge until ready to serve.
2. Split and toast the mini bagels, spread with the salmon mixture and serve.
Salmon tastes delicious in this crispy, herby fishcake.
